{"tid":1915532,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"凱婷真身!!! (多圖）p.s. 同佢地同一間中學","createTime":"2020-03-08T09:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T14:46:57.000Z","uid":62648,"like":521,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"12dfa899eaaf1b55c389b4ae63e0b7d2fc6b6eec","tid":1915532,"uid":62648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:24:17.000Z","msg":"話說見到上網講返起凱婷哩單野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MC8Mxr1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMC8Mxr1.jpg&h=deefa7d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我估好多人都唔知佢哋係咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，哩個先係打篇野個個女仔（哩張係佢以前個樣）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ZMioxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ZMioxB.jpg&h=48c74438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢依加大個左係咁樣：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4pLGmjO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4pLGmjO.jpg&h=8ac3a155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後哩個係凱婷：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6N843yU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6N843yU.jpg&h=0955efb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n凱婷依加婚都結埋 仲生左個女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢個女唔係牛丸 希望大家唔好搞錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vNo1mnF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvNo1mnF.jpg&h=ec10a809&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n凱婷同埋打篇野個個女仔都仲好好朋友的（左邊個凱婷 右邊係打個篇野個女仔）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QkeozFN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQkeozFN.jpg&h=05a93d2b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oeReGkO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoeReGkO.jpg&h=3f05cb42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3年前.. 佢地都未知自己會紅爆網絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BFxhD74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBFxhD74.jpg&h=fcd61ec3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：同佢地同一間中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個時都估唔到佢地會紅到依加都仲有人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前見到連登有人嘗試起底 但起錯哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想解開大家心目中嘅疑團"},{"pid":"5a36b21268cdbd6787e6a0b899c623a3c1155dfb","tid":1915532,"uid":12514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5f342ed4e84525f25f2c420f44e6c46a3587a4","tid":1915532,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:25:35.000Z","msg":"LM 不推文"},{"pid":"9ea78bc1ff66855f3d69cde2c449e7138db509a0","tid":1915532,"uid":1971,"like":141,"dislike":13,"score":128,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"咪搞人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d913257acc7945cc56eae89cb122dfe28525cf1a","tid":1915532,"uid":112748,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:26:03.000Z","msg":"who?"},{"pid":"44b957cf4e1b544883205dcee46b7d7aef596c56","tid":1915532,"uid":30927,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:28:33.000Z","msg":"想知佢地戒左煙未"},{"pid":"f79c35ca522811d5cd0bd62bdaff780563de44f7","tid":1915532,"uid":3270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:29:04.000Z","msg":"On"},{"pid":"a84a16f162acfa80326d070a413ad79341b5c35a","tid":1915532,"uid":55010,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:29:37.000Z","msg":"邊位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be22433bb5b32815459d13963ddd4a6e8c3f29e4","tid":1915532,"uid":74778,"like":136,